<p>
Thanks to my resolution to fret less, I'm spending
less time on childcare (A+) and more time
exploring my own interests (Discretionary -
Productive). I've even been doing a little less
consulting. It feels good. I'm still around in
case she wants help, but now I get to explore
things I want to do.
</p>

<p>
Let's break that discretionary/consulting time down:
